<item>
            <title>[SEC-594] LDAP BindAuthenticator does not set password in user details</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-594</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The method BindAuthenticator.bindWithDn does not set the password in the user details. &lt;br/&gt;
Add at line 90:&lt;br/&gt;
            user.setPassword(password);&lt;/p&gt;</description>
